snippet.title: PAYDAY 3: Syntax Error Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Free for all Silver & Gold owners, Syntax Error is the first new original heist coming to PAYDAY 3. Add to that a packed weapon pack and tailor pack and you got a recipe for some serious crime.
Check out the Syntax Error Bundle, out now!

Syntax Error website: https://t.paydaythegame.com/c/f18npt
